<h1>Installation</h1>

<p>To install Design System you can use <a target="_blank" href="https://docs.npmjs.com/">NPM</a>:</p>
<pre>npm install Wikia/design-system --save</pre>
<p>It is advised to use <code class="format-code">--save</code> to add it to your package.json.</p>

<section>
	<h2>How to install SVG</h2>
	<p>
		Read more about how to handle SVG on {{#link-to 'overview.svg-assets'}}SVG Assets{{/link-to}} page.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>How to install SCSS</h2>
	<p>This is a preferred way of using Design System as this installs both styles and variables.</p>
	<p>
		To use SCSS files in your project include
		<a target="_blank"
		   href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/scss/index.scss">dist/scss/index.scss</a>
		in your main SCSS file:

		{{#code-sample language='scss'}}@import "path/to/design-system/dist/scss/index"{{/code-sample}}

		Note that
		<a target="_blank"
		   href="https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer">autoprefixer</a> is required for SCSS compilation,
		as there are no prefixes in SCSS files.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>How to install CSS</h2>
	<p>
		If you can't use SASS or prefer to use CSS, you can include
		<a target="_blank"
		   href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/css/styles.css">dist/css/styles.css</a>
		in your project:
	</p>
	<pre>path/to/design-system/dist/css/styles.css</pre>
	<p>
		Note that compiled CSS for Design System include prefixes managed by autoprefixer and
		targets 4 last versions of major browsers. As configured here:
		<a target="_blank"
		   href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/ember-cli-build.js">ember-cli-build.js</a>
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>How to include SASS variables</h2>
	<p>This step is not needed if you import SCSS files.</p>
	<p>
		To import SASS variables import
		<a target="_blank"
		   href="https://github.com/Wikia/design-system/blob/master/dist/scss/wds-variables/index.scss"
		>dist/scss/wds-variables/index.scss</a>:
		{{#code-sample language='scss'}}
@import "path/to/design-system/dist/scss/wds-variables/index"
		{{/code-sample}}
	</p>
</section>
